title: QINTENT-ELECTRIC: Feedback-Induced Flow in Quantum Circuits
description: This dataset presents experimental and theoretical resources associated with the study of electricity-like informational flows induced by structural feedback in quantum circuits. It includes the full research manuscript (markdown and PDF), Jupyter notebooks demonstrating entropy-shift simulations, and selected dialogues reflecting the experimental design process.
notes: All data and results are generated using Qiskit 1.0.2. Figures are derived directly from experimental simulations. Authors retain anonymity for the purpose of structural objectivity in interpretation.
